      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ALLINTHETIMING (2) was a long way back last start but hit the line well to finish a close fourth over 1300m at Wangaratta. Looks suited here and rates a major contender. EMERALD REWARD (1) also went back early from his wide draw here last time but hit the line strongly to finish fifth. Drawn much kinder this time for Crowther, who sticks, and is well placed to land a long-awaited winning blow. HASTA LA CHILLY (5) registered a strong win at Naracoorte two runs ago. Not disgraced last time out when third over 1200m at Murray Bridge, beaten 1.1 lengths. Peaking now fourth-up and can find his way back in the winners' circle. SILVER CLIFF (3) finished fourth when first-up from a spell last start over 1100m at Warrnambool after racing on the pace for much of the way. Better for that and will prove tougher to reel in this time, if they opt to roll forward again. LONELY ONE (7) is mixing her form but turned in a strong showing here last time when beaten a head. Keeping safe.",
